    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. so basically, what you're saying is that the main reason people argue against density is just because they're worried about things like gentrification? it seems like the \"anti-density\" crowd is mostly just using those concerns to block progress that would actually help the environment and the economy.",
